At per sampling site, 20 L quantitative water samples of zooplankton were collected using 64 μm mesh size net from a bottom depth,
 just above the sediment, and at the surface (i.e., 0.5 m) were passed in the field. In the laboratory, three quantitative samples of zooplankton
 from the Yangtze River were further mixed and filteredthrough 5-μm microporous filter paper (Millipore)
